===Noun===
'''rig'''

# {{nautical}} The [[arrangement]] of [[mast]]s, [[spar]]s, and sails on a [[sailing]] [[vessel]].
# [[special|Special]] equipment or [[gear]] used for a [[particular]] [[purpose]].
# {{US}} A [[truck]] or [[tractor]].
# The special [[apparatus]] used for [[drilling]] [[oil]] [[wells]].
# {{informal}} A costume or an outfit.
# {{computing}} {{slang}} Computer [[case]], often modified for [[looks]].

